modName: Autumn Sun Cottage - A Tiny Home
summary: A cozy little home in the Rift. Plenty of custom storage and unique clutter all in a compact one room home. Large garden and full forge outside. Adoption friendly.
descriptionHtml:
[center][color=#e69138][b][size=6]Autumn Sun Cottage[/size][/b][/color][color=#ff0000]
[size=4][b][color=#ffd966]A Cozy Little House Mod[/color][/b][/size][/color][/center][color=#ff0000][color=#ffd966]

[/color][/color][color=#f1c232][u][b][size=5]About this Mod:
[/size][/b][/u][/color][size=4]Autumn Sun Cottage is a very small house mod with personality. Lots of clutter placed in this single room home gives a sense that someone actually lives here.[/size]
[color=#ff0000]
[/color][u][b][color=#ffd966][size=5]Features:[/size][/color][/b][/u]

[size=4]-> Custom storage
-> Arcane Enchanter
-> Alchemy Lab
-> 3 Unique Weapon Plaques
-> Lots of unique clutter
-> Cooking Pot
-> 51 Plantable Spots
-> Full forge outside
-> Adoption friendly (Up to 2 kids)
-> Tiny stables
-> A few chickens, a cow, and some goats
-> Small pond[/size]

[size=5][u][b][color=#ffd966]Requirements:

[/color][/b][/u][size=4]Skyrim Up-to-date
Dragonborn
Hearthfires[/size][/size]

[u][b][color=#ffd966][size=5]Location:[/size][/color][/b][/u]

[size=4]The Rift[/size]

[u][b][color=#ffd966][size=5]Note:
[/size][/color][/b][/u]
A few pictures were taken before the final version was created. Some things may have been moved or replaced compared to some pictures. (The planters by the alchemy table, the second wardrobe above the bed)
